Docs.summary: The DecoderParams class contains decoder parameters that are used by multiple decoder symbologies. The property provides access to such decoder parameters as Enabled and IsSupported, among others. NOTE: When calling enable() after disable(), all the latest configuration parameter values (Config.DecoderParams, Config.ScannerParams, Config.ReaderParams and Config.InterfaceParams) will be set automatically.
